Key to map mockup:
Terrain layer: blue = sea, brown = shore, green = land (progressively redder for higher relief), light blue = rivers.
Cities layer: grey = built-up area.
Flak layer: magenta block = flak unit (w/ radar and/or searchlight control).
Target layer: red crosshair = A.P. (Aiming Point).
Weather layer: grey = cloud.
Route layer: black = route & turning points.
Aircraft layer: white = bomber, yellow = crashed bomber, cyan = damaged bomber (includes mech.fail), red = fighter, orange = crashed fighter.
